text.section:
An affidavit of severance shall contain or be accompanied by:
A statement identifying the owner of the real property from which the manufactured home is to be severed, including the name, residence, and mailing address of the owner;
A description of the manufactured home, including the name of the manufacturer, the make, model name, model year, dimensions, manufacturer's serial number, and a statement whether the manufactured home is new or used;
The liber and folio number for and the recordation date of the affidavit of affixation for the manufactured home; and
A statement by an attorney admitted to practice law in the State, or a title insurance producer licensed by the State, that states that the manufactured home and the real property from which the manufactured home is to be severed are free and clear of any lien, security interest, or encumbrance.
